Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:12.03,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(4000,1)}Iadul sunt ceilalți
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:12.03,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}Jean-Paul Sartre, "Cu ușile închise"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așteaptă!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Antropologul Edward Hall a împărțit spațiul personal în patru zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Una din acele zone este "spațiul \Nintim", cu "etapa de izolare" acolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Această distanța este destul de \Nmică încât să accepți pe altcineva
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}și mulți se opun încălcării ei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Totuși, este mult prea tare!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oricum, există și excepții.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:40.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nu chiar, mie-mi cam place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:41.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Îmi place ceva mai moale—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}De exemplu, Kushida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:45.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ați văzut o fată cu ochelari?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiar dacă se apropie foarte mult, ea reușește să nu declanșeze reacția spațiului personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și totuși, Sakura i s-a opus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Îi este teamă de legături.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}De asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}își ține privirea în pământ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze că v-am făcut să \Nveniți cu mine pentru asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt cea care ar trebui să-și ceară scuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu ți-am stricat camera foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nu, eu ar trebui să fiu mai atentă...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Asta este așa de drăguță!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergi la magazinul de electronice \Ndin mall ca să îți repari camera foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar chiar aveai nevoie de mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De fapt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of, privește. Asta nu e bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.58,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Tejgheaua pentru asistență tehnică
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Este o problemă de pornire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, asta nu e bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai garanție la ea? Garanția...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai adus garanția?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:28.22,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Nou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, încă este în perioada de garanție.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partea stricată poate fi... \Nînlocuită... fără a plăti ceva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Înțeleg de ce îi este greu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lui Sakura, căreia îi este teamă de străini, să vorbească cu acest tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Presupun că voia putere în număr.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ne poți spune cât va dura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Două sau trei zile. Da, două sau trei zile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poți completa acest formular?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.50,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Chitanța obiectului pentru reparare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avem nevoie de adresă, nume și...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,număr de telefon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îl pot împrumuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Când reparațiile sunt gata, te rog să mă contactezi pe mine în schimb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hei, tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Camera îi aparține ei, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu sunt sigur că putem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Garanția producătorului confirmă locația și data cumpărării.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai spus că este valabilă acum câteva secunde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-mi pot imagina cum ar putea fi o problemă legală.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Ești sigur?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, vom face așa, atunci.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumesc pentru că m-ați ajutat astăzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu e nicio problemă. Oricum, fusese vina mea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar, Sakura-san, poți vorbi cu normal cu noi, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suntem în același an.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, ai folosit numai limbajul formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am... S-Sigur. Voi încerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu trebuie nici să te forțezi s-o faci.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sunt bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În regulă.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scuzați-mă o clipă, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voi merge până la toaletă. {I'm gonna go freshen up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's awkward being alone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce e în neregulă, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something you wanted to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think would \Nbe the best thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding Sudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should do whatever you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't say anything, \NI think I'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your eyes weren't scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's hard to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you need advice, \NKushida would be more amicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's grateful, but for some reason, \Nshe can't fully trust Kushida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what it seems like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you would regret it \Nif you didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that's the only answer you need, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For Sudo." "For Kushida."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For my classmates."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw away all of those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw them all... away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to burden \Nyourself with all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should testify for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For my... sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, think we should call it a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I come by your room later, Ayanokoji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you need to come \Nall the way to my room for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was actually looking some things \Nup on the Internet earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this girl look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say just from the \Nface and the build, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture was taken in one of our dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought it was strange that \NSakura wore fake eyeglasses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no distortion behind the lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she's trying to hide her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why she wouldn't testify?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.52,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,New Messages: 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.52,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Sakura Airi\NThis is Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says she might be able \Nto help with Sudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess going with her today was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad she decided to trust \Nus, but I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayanokoji-kun, isn't there \Nanything you're trying to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.05,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(381,1)}Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.05,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(298,1)}At this school, class membership remains the same from enrollment through graduation.\NIt is assumed that the students of each class will come together to overcome\Nvarious challenges and grow through doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.30,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Student Council Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've sent out the notification \Nfor the arbitration hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between Class 1-D and 1-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Class D...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you spend your day off with Kushida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because of the thing with Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though we couldn't get her word that \Nshe would share what she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you have quite the \Nexpression on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? I don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how I always look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I am impressed by how \Nself-serving you've been lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hesitate when I ask you for a favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when Kushida-san asks, \Nyou comply immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm attempting to analyze,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,rationally and carefully, the factors \Nthat account for the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more important is that the \Nstudent council's picked the day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for Sudo-kun's hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:09:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.58,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Student Council Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will now hold deliberations \Nregarding the violent incident
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that occurred last Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Student Council Secretary, \NI, Tachibana, will preside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The student council president, \Ncoming in over a little brawl like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonders never cease, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to my busy schedule, there are some \Nagendas I'm forced to miss participating in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a rule, though, I do attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's just a coincidence, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wasn't expecting the \Npresident to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Horikita can't bring out her full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To both sides: I wish to ascertain which \Nversion of the events is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komiya and the other two,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you insist you were called to the special \Nannex by Sudo and then attacked by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sudo denies this. He insists that Komiya \Nwas the one who called him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your versions of the \Nevents are contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one fact we can be certain of:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the aggressor, Sudo, \Ninjured Komiya, Kondo, and Ishizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll admit that I hit them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they're the ones who started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't recall doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having the main discussion \Nbe about the injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You damn well did! \NI was only defending myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and giving Sudo free rein \Nare both bad for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horikita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You just kept running your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're jealous because I'm on \Nthe list of potential regulars!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And at basketball practice, \Nyou always get in my—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silence, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without new testimony or evidence, \Nwe will proceed under these assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems there was no need for discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's clear from the state of their injuries \Nthat the violence was one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe I should base my decision on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Class D's insistence that it was \Nself-defense is contradicted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by Sudo-kun's lack of injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the condition of \NIshizaki-kun and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it! What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When someone's spacing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a strong physical stimulus will \Nsnap them back to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't fight, we're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to question the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were the circumstances under \Nwhich Sudo-kun called you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After practice ended, he said \Nhe wanted to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what was Ishizaki-kun doing \Nin the special annex with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is not in the basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no reason for him to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... wanted insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows what a violent guy \NSudo-kun is. He's a big guy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought he might attack you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a prepared response.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so you brought Ishizaki-kun, \Nwho had a reputation as being a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,strong fighter in middle school, \Nas a bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it to protect myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some knowledge of martial arts myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fighting multiple enemies increases \Nthe difficulty exponentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you to be beaten so one-sidedly,\Nespecially with Ishizaki-kun present,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... that's just because \Nwe didn't want a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had no desire to fight, \Nand you weren't fighting back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's extremely unlikely that \Nall three of you would be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That does sound like common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Common sense doesn't apply \Nwhen Sudo-kun's involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an incredibly violent man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a student who \Nwitnessed the entire fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would the witness step forward, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would the witness please state her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Class 1-D, Sakura Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Class C students attacked Sudo-kun first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really did see it, \Nwhy didn't you step forward sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you Class Ds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just... telling the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun. Sakura Airi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not being forced \Nto lie for the sake of your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To save Sudo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that Sakura-san is here proves \Nthat she really did witness the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't, she wouldn't be sitting here, \Neven if we'd asked her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we just needed someone \Nto make a statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't you think I would \Nhave chosen someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you chose to use someone \Nlike her to lend further credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Credibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop twisting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura-san came here in good faith—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop taking advantage of your well-meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but weak-willed classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is not what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at her trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't put any more burden on—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do have... proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't dig this hole any deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is proof that I was in \Nthe special annex that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Display it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day... I was looking for somewhere \Ndeserted to take pictures of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dates on a digital camera \Ncan easily be altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rather insubstantial, as proof goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Sakagami, this picture is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you will believe \Nthat I was there that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you were telling the \Ntruth about being present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know who instigated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't prove that you saw \Neverything that went down, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might I propose a compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite your pictures, \Nyou have no definitive proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it does appear that the Class C \Nstudents may bear some responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A two-week suspension for Sudo-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a one-week suspension for the \NClass C students. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The difference in punishment is based \Non the difference in harm done to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without Sakura's testimony and evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sudo's suspension would \Nhave been a month or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is quite a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Chabashira, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the conclusion \Nhas already been reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura, you did very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Class D representative Horikita-san, \Nplease tell us your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that Sudo-kun, the instigator \Nof this incident, has a serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He never thinks about the trouble that his \Ndaily actions will cause those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidents like this are inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to realize that it's your \Nattitude that's at the root of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should reflect, \Nbut not about this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean that he should re-evaluate \Nthe person he has been in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horikita?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In regards to the incident \Nwe're discussing right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that Sudo-kun is free of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this was not an unfortunate incident \Nthat just happened to take place,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but an intentional set-up \Ninstigated by Class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assert Sudo-kun's complete \Ninnocence in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An intentional set-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the president's little sister is—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the witness testified, \NSudo-kun is a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please make the correct judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the victims, Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up! Listen up—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, this was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything you say is completely at odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that one side \Nis offering false testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me ask Class C... Can you \Nsay with absolute certainty that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your testimony here today is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Class D?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give my judgment tomorrow at 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I receive no proof \Nof your opponents' lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or admissions of your own guilt by then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be putting expulsion \Non the table, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:57.11,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Drawing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to lose. I don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have just spoken up from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I didn't have... the courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold your head high, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.25,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you showed up with Suzune, \NI assumed you had some strategy in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm neither Zhuge Liang \Nnor Kuroda Kanbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Suzune went rogue in proclaiming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his innocence, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a wild idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't prove it, it's just a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mask is nothing but a shackle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I only told the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good question.
